108
00:06:46,763 --> 00:06:47,896
-Hi, everybody.

109
00:06:47,929 --> 00:06:49,963
-Ah, Miss Ochi.

110
00:06:49,996 --> 00:06:52,729
MISATO OCHI: All right, get
to your seats every one.

111
00:06:52,763 --> 00:06:53,829
