at Urahara's shop,

208
00:11:17,284 --> 00:11:18,917
and it's not going
to cost us a dime.

209
00:11:18,950 --> 00:11:21,017
The least we should
do is try not

210
00:11:21,050 --> 00:11:23,850
to take up space and
cause a lot of trouble.

211
00:11:23,884 --> 00:11:25,784
-What was it that made
you all decide to come

212
00:11:25,817 --> 00:11:27,284
and live here with us?

213
00:11:27,317 --> 00:11:29,250
