Bounts are gone,

215
00:11:31,284 --> 00:11:33,850
are roles have come to an end.

216
00:11:33,884 --> 00:11:36,217
-Plus, Ichigo and the others
spend their entire day

217
00:11:36,250 --> 00:11:36,950
at school.

218
00:11:36,984 --> 00:11:38,784
