live here instead.

221
00:11:43,884 --> 00:11:46,250
-We can see them
whenever we like.

222
00:11:46,284 --> 00:11:47,817
-Oh, now I understand.

223
00:11:47,850 --> 00:11:49,550
Ah, that hurts!

224
00:11:49,584 --> 00:11:50,250
