225
00:11:50,284 --> 00:11:51,850
Please stop!

226
00:11:51,884 --> 00:11:53,584
-Why'd you have to ask the
most obvious questions?

227
00:11:53,617 --> 00:11:54,484
Can't you figure it out?

228
00:11:54,517 --> 00:11:56,150
