make sense yet?

230
00:11:57,984 --> 00:11:59,917
They should help out
around here from now on.

231
00:11:59,950 --> 00:12:01,184
-Don't fight.

232
00:12:01,217 --> 00:12:03,950
Let's all try to
get along together.

233
00:12:03,984 --> 00:12:04,750
-Quiet.

234
00:12:04,784 --> 00:12:07,850
I'm trying to read.

235
00:12:07,884 --> 00:12:09,584
MISATO OCHI: Pay
attention, everyone.

236
00:12:09,617 --> 00:12:12,750
The transfer student I told
you about earlier is here.

237
00:12:12,784 --> 00:12:14,584
