introduce yourself?

238
00:12:14,617 --> 00:12:16,717
-There's he, as in
the flat footed.

239
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:20,217
The ko from Imoko Onono,
that old politician.

240
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:24,517
