248
00:12:39,584 --> 00:12:40,284
SHINJI: Oh, Miss Ochi?

249
00:12:40,317 --> 00:12:41,784
MISATO OCHI: What?

250
00:12:41,817 --> 00:12:42,417
SHINJI: I'd like to sit
next to a cute girl.

251
00:12:42,450 --> 00:12:43,250
MISATO OCHI: A cute girl?

252
00:12:43,284 --> 00:12:44,784
-Uryu.

253
00:12:44,817 --> 00:12:48,884
I thought that you would
have recovered by now.

254
00:12:48,917 --> 00:12:50,717
But I guess your
powers won't come back

255
00:12:50,750 --> 00:12:53,284
as easily as I imagined.

256
00:12:53,317 --> 00:12:55,717
MISATO OCHI: I think
better have you sit there.

257
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:56,222
-OK.

258
00:12:59,084 --> 00:13:01,684
