going to be neighbors.

259
00:13:01,717 --> 00:13:02,750
Yeah.

260
00:13:02,784 --> 00:13:06,050
I hope we can be
friends, Ichigo.

261
00:13:06,084 --> 00:13:07,117
-Oh, yeah.

262
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:08,084
Yeah, sure thing.

263
00:13:08,117 --> 00:13:13,817
[shinji chuckles]

264
00:13:13,850 --> 00:13:16,117
-No, I don't want to
live like this anymore.

265
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:20,950
I want to go out and meet
girls with bodacious bodies.

266
00:13:20,984 --> 00:13:23,750
A cute little guy like me
would be a chick magnet.

267
00:13:23,784 --> 00:13:25,650
But I'm stuck inside.

268
00:13:25,684 --> 00:13:27,917
-You'd look even better
with a sock in your mouth.

269
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:30,850
Be quiet, or everyone in the
whole house will hear you.

270
00:13:30,884 --> 00:13:33,517
-You're just jealous
because you're not cuddly.

271
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:36,184
One way or the other, this party
animal is getting out of here.

272
00:13:36,217 --> 00:13:38,017
This town better lock
up all the ladies,

273
00:13:38,050 --> 00:13:40,584
and this lion ain't lying.

274
00:13:40,617 --> 00:13:44,550
To be perfectly frank, if I
may, you're a pain in the butt.

275
00:13:44,584 --> 00:13:45,917
I miss being in your body.

276
00:13:45,950 --> 00:13:47,717
All that peeping in
windows and under skirts

277
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:49,217
didn't ruin my reputation.

278
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:51,650
It only ruined yours.

279
00:13:51,684 --> 00:13:52,884
-Dammit, Kon.

280
00:13:52,917 --> 00:13:55,050
That had better be a joke.

281
00:13:55,084 --> 00:13:57,050
Don't tell me that you were
doing something illegal

282
00:13:57,084 --> 00:13:58,717
out there.

283
00:13:58,750 --> 00:14:00,984
-Being locked up was bearable
when Rukia was around.

284
00:14:01,017 --> 00:14:02,817
Oh, Rukia, please come back.

285
00:14:02,850 --> 00:14:04,584
Please come back!

286
00:14:04,617 --> 00:14:05,250
Come back!

287
00:14:05,284 --> 00:14:06,617
-Quiet, Kon!

288
00:14:06,650 --> 00:14:09,750
I'm tired of hearing
you complain!

289
00:14:09,784 --> 00:14:13,550
[medallion buzzes]

290
00:14:13,584 --> 00:14:14,784
-Oh, that's just great.

291
00:14:22,717 --> 00:14:23,484
He goes.

292
00:14:23,517 --> 00:14:24,984
I always worry
what kind of shape

293
00:14:25,017 --> 00:14:27,750
my body will be in
when I get back.

294
00:14:27,784 --> 00:14:29,950
Try not to get my body arrested.

295
00:14:29,984 --> 00:14:32,917
And behave.

296
00:14:32,950 --> 00:14:33,950
-Goodbye.

297
00:14:33,984 --> 00:14:36,050
Take your time.

298
00:14:36,084 --> 00:14:40,750
Ah, it's been awhile since
I've been inside this body.

299
00:14:40,784 --> 00:14:44,950
It's time to go out, get
down, get funky, and par-tay.

300
00:14:44,984 --> 00:14:47,584
[hollow howls]

301
00:14:47,617 --> 00:14:49,017
-Looks like Halloween
must have come early.

302
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:58,984
Those damn things.

303
00:14:59,017 --> 00:15:00,917
They just keep getting
uglier all the time.

304
00:15:03,784 --> 00:15:04,717
-Hey, wait!

305
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:08,284
Why are you dressed
up like a Soul Reaper?

306
00:15:08,317 --> 00:15:09,750
I see you.

307
00:15:09,784 --> 00:15:11,950
What are you up to?

308
00:15:11,984 --> 00:15:12,884
-Who the hell are you?

309
00:15:12,917 --> 00:15:13,366
-What?

310
00:15:13,366 --> 00:15:14,899
Who am I?

311
00:15:14,932 --> 00:15:17,599
I'm Zennosuke Kurumadani.

312
00:15:17,632 --> 00:15:20,732
Miss Rukia Kuchiki had a
little trouble with the law,

313
00:15:20,766 --> 00:15:23,799
so an elite Soul Reaper was
left in charge of the area.

314
00:15:23,832 --> 00:15:26,799
So tell me, are you shaking yet?

315
00:15:26,832 --> 00:15:30,832
-I'm Ichigo Kurosaki,
substitute Soul Reaper.

316
00:15:30,866 --> 00:15:34,266
Look, this is my pass.

317
00:15:34,299 --> 00:15:35,866
-Combat pass?

318
00:15:35,899 --> 00:15:38,666
No way.

319
00:15:38,699 --> 00:15:41,199
Ha ha ha ha, that's funny.

320
00:15:41,232 --> 00:15:42,166
A combat pass?

321
00:15:42,199 --> 00:15:43,899
Give me a break, kid.

322
00:15:43,932 --> 00:15:45,899
Who do you think you're
fooling with that thing?

323
00:15:45,932 --> 00:15:47,232
-What's with this?

324
00:15:47,266 --> 00:15:50,166
This damn thing is
completely useless.

325
00:15:50,199 --> 00:15:51,799
-Come on, say something.

326
00:15:51,832 --> 00:15:53,799
If you want to apologize,
now's your chance.

327
00:15:59,799 --> 00:16:05,732
[shinji chuckles]

328
00:16:05,766 --> 00:16:11,999
[zennosuke gasps]

329
00:16:12,032 --> 00:16:13,999
-Dammit.

330
00:16:14,032 --> 00:16:16,999
Hirako.

331
00:16:17,032 --> 00:16:20,299
Is that a zanpakuto?

332
00:16:20,332 --> 00:16:22,999
Who the hell are you?

333
00:16:23,032 --> 00:16:24,932
-Shh.

334
00:16:24,966 --> 00:16:29,966
You mustn't make too much
noise, Ichigo Kurosaki.

335
00:16:29,999 --> 00:16:32,599
Those who have spiritual
pressure like you possess

336
00:16:32,632 --> 00:16:36,032
need to learn how to stay calm.

337
00:16:36,066 --> 00:16:39,999
Or your presence will be felt.

338
00:16:40,032 --> 00:16:41,232
-Felt by who?

339
00:16:41,266 --> 00:16:42,932
Who will feel it?

340
00:16:42,966 --> 00:16:45,799
-It seems I need everything
to be out in open

341
00:16:45,832 --> 00:16:48,066
for you to understand it.

342
00:16:48,099 --> 00:16:49,732
Children are so
foolish and blind.

343
00:17:03,232 --> 00:17:04,366
-That was weird.

344
00:17:04,399 --> 00:17:06,632
What a strange sound.

345
00:17:06,666 --> 00:17:08,966
I thought that Ichigo found
me for a second there.

346
00:17:08,999 --> 00:17:11,232
It's a perfect night
to get into trouble.

347
00:17:11,266 --> 00:17:13,166
Better lock up the ladies,
because here I come.

348
00:17:13,199 --> 00:17:15,132
I'm a party animal!

349
00:17:15,166 --> 00:17:17,166
I won't get Ichigo's
body arrested,

350
00:17:17,199 --> 00:17:18,799
but I do plan to wear it out.

351
00:17:37,132 --> 00:17:39,766
-Ichigo Kurosaki.

352
00:17:47,732 --> 00:17:49,632
-It's a hollow.

353
00:17:49,666 --> 00:17:51,799
It's huge.

354
00:17:51,832 --> 00:17:55,032
I wonder if that could
be a Menos Grande.

355
00:17:55,066 --> 00:17:57,266
It tore open the sky
and came through.

356
00:18:02,899 --> 00:18:03,866
-What the hell?

357
00:18:03,899 --> 00:18:05,332
What was that about?

358
00:18:05,366 --> 00:18:10,066
Something almost blasted me
right out of Ichigo's body.

359
00:18:10,099 --> 00:18:11,699
What?

360
00:18:11,732 --> 00:18:15,666
-I hope you haven't forgotten
me, Ichigo Kurosaki.

361
00:18:21,266 --> 00:18:24,299
-No, no it couldn't be.

362
00:18:24,332 --> 00:18:26,099
It's Grand Fisher!

363
00:18:41,799 --> 00:18:44,032
-This spiritual pressure,
it's so powerful.

364
00:18:44,066 --> 00:18:47,999
What is it?

365
00:18:48,032 --> 00:18:52,099
Those guys are
monsters, both of them.

366
00:18:52,132 --> 00:18:52,999
-It's here.

367
00:18:53,032 --> 00:18:55,099
-Who the hell are you?

368
00:18:55,132 --> 00:18:58,199
Hirako, answer me!

369
00:18:58,232 --> 00:18:59,832
-I explained it.

370
00:18:59,866 --> 00:19:01,266
You're the one to blame.

371
00:19:01,299 --> 00:19:03,099
It's all because
you were releasing

372
00:19:03,132 --> 00:19:04,632
your spiritual pressure.

373
00:19:04,666 --> 00:19:08,232
-I demand that you
tell me who you are.

374
00:19:08,266 --> 00:19:10,232
-You're a pain, you know that?

375
00:19:10,266 --> 00:19:13,699
With all that's going on,
you only care who I am?

376
00:19:13,732 --> 00:19:14,799
Then take a good look.

377
00:19:22,966 --> 00:19:24,832
What do you see?

378
00:19:24,866 --> 00:19:25,832
Tell me.

379
00:19:28,966 --> 00:19:31,666
Try and guess, if you can.

380
00:19:31,699 --> 00:19:32,832
-A Hollow mask.

381
00:19:32,866 --> 00:19:34,132
-Yes.

382
00:19:34,166 --> 00:19:37,999
A zanpakuto and a Hollow mask.

383
00:19:38,032 --> 00:19:38,732
You get it now?

384
00:19:43,066 --> 00:19:46,766
I'm a soul reaper
who crossed over

385
00:19:46,799 --> 00:19:49,966
into the realm of the Hollows.

386
00:19:49,999 --> 00:19:52,832
You remember what
I told you, right?

387
00:19:52,866 --> 00:19:55,732
I hope we can be friend, Ichigo.

388
00:19:55,766 --> 00:19:58,132
-Oh, yeah.

389
00:19:58,166 --> 00:20:01,899
-You see, I'm a Visored.

390
00:20:01,932 --> 00:20:02,899
You're one of us, Ichigo.

391
00:20:05,932 --> 00:20:10,099
You do not belong with them.

392
00:20:10,132 --> 00:20:13,166
You have got to know that you
do not along with them at all.

393
00:20:22,366 --> 00:20:25,066
-What incredible
spiritual pressure he has.

394
00:20:25,099 --> 00:20:27,132
Is he really a Menos Grande?

395
00:20:27,166 --> 00:20:31,032
Well, it doesn't
matter in the end.

396
00:20:31,066 --> 00:20:34,966
I can still fight, even with
my diminished spiritual energy.

397
00:20:34,999 --> 00:20:35,732
I am not helpless.

398
00:20:38,932 --> 00:20:50,099
Take this! [inaudible] I filled
those ginto with spirit energy

399
00:20:50,132 --> 00:20:52,299
when I was in the Soul Society.

400
00:20:52,332 --> 00:20:55,132
They may not be
enough to kill him.

401
00:20:55,166 --> 00:20:57,166
But maybe I'll be able
to discourage him.

402
00:21:00,166 --> 00:21:00,999
Instant regeneration.

403
00:21:13,632 --> 00:21:16,799
His upper body disappeared.

404
00:21:16,832 --> 00:21:19,299
It split in two.

405
00:21:19,332 --> 00:21:21,299
No, there were two of them.

406
00:21:29,332 --> 00:21:40,899
[uryu gasps in pain]

407
00:21:40,932 --> 00:21:44,732
[hollow roars]

408
00:21:44,766 --> 00:21:45,732
-My, my.

409
00:21:50,766 --> 00:21:54,132
How clumsy.

410
00:21:54,166 --> 00:21:56,766
Uryu.

411
00:21:56,799 --> 00:21:57,366
-So it's you.

412
00:22:00,732 --> 00:22:01,999
Ryuken.

413
00:22:02,032 --> 00:22:04,766
-Is that any way to
address your father?

414
00:22:04,799 --> 00:22:07,866
You haven't changed
at all, have you, son?

415
00:22:17,295 --> 00:22:19,162
[MUSIC -- MAI HOSHIMURA, "CHERRY
BLOSSOM WEATHER"]

416
00:23:46,924 --> 00:23:49,591
-I didn't know that Uryu's
father was a Quincy.

417
00:23:49,624 --> 00:23:52,091
-Does that mean his father
wears those goofy clothes, too?

418
00:23:52,124 --> 00:23:53,157
-Of course.

419
00:23:53,191 --> 00:23:55,091
Those clothes are the
traditional Quincy attire.

420
00:23:55,124 --> 00:23:56,857
-You and your father
are both Quincys?

421
00:23:56,891 --> 00:23:57,924
That's awful.

422
00:23:57,957 --> 00:23:59,091
-Don't be such a hypocrite.

423
00:23:59,124 --> 00:24:00,091
What?

424
00:24:00,124 --> 00:24:01,157
-It's a secret.

425
00:24:01,191 --> 00:24:03,024
[MUSIC -- MAI HOSHIMURA, "CHERRY
BLOSSOM WEATHER"]

426
00:24:12,857 --> 00:24:15,091
-Glad you saw me first!

427
00:24:15,124 --> 00:24:16,057
-Hello?

428
00:24:16,091 --> 00:24:17,224
What in the world is
going on in this town?

429
00:24:17,257 --> 00:24:19,924
Some of the weirdest people
I've ever known live here.

430
00:24:19,957 --> 00:24:21,957
And there are people
who can see me.

431
00:24:21,991 --> 00:24:24,524
Even a substitute
soul reaper showed up!

432
00:24:24,557 --> 00:24:25,724
-I'm sorry.

433
00:24:25,757 --> 00:24:27,524
Due to the disruption
in the Zerrete,

434
00:24:27,557 --> 00:24:28,757
we were delayed
in informing you.

435
00:24:28,791 --> 00:24:30,124
-What do you mean, delayed?

436
00:24:30,157 --> 00:24:33,457
-Uh, continue to focus
on the lesser Hollows.

437
00:24:33,491 --> 00:24:34,891
-What Hollows?

438
00:24:34,924 --> 00:24:39,891
-And stay out the way of
the substitute Soul Reaper.

439
00:24:39,924 --> 00:24:43,057
-I used to be a
somebody in this town.

